## Description {#details}

Template metafunction to get the parent type for a symbol table list.

Implementations create a typedef called <code>type</code> so that we only need a single template parameter for the list and traits.

Definition at line 47 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/ir/symboltablelisttraits-h">SymbolTableListTraits.h</a>.
